casebody.data:
Martha Cares OLSEN, Fritz Olsen, Robert E. Lehrer, Sheribel F. Rothenberg, Stephen Casey, Kathleen Casey, Ernest Lewis MacVicar, III, Janice MacVicar, Ronald Devlam, and Michelle Devlam, Appellants,
v.
JUDE AND REED, LLC, Appellee. SC: 158238-9
COA: 337724, 337726 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 3, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
